      "review_summary": "The PR routes OpenShell local mirror mkdir, remove, and rename through fs-safe root-confined operations and adds regression tests for rebinding and cross-root rename cases.\n\nPR surface: Source +198, Tests +317. Total +515 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: the PR deletes the remote path first, then `removeRootRelative()` calls `Root.stat()`, and fs-safe v0.3.0 rejects symlink leaves in `Root.stat()` before `Root.remove()` can safely unlink them.",
